### Login (Required for standalone execution)
# @name login
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{jsonContentType}}

{
  "email": "{{superAdminRoleTestEmail}}",
  "password": "{{superAdminRoleTestPassword}}"
}

###
@authToken = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### List Teams
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/teams
Content-Type: {{jsonContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create Team
# @name createTeam
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/teams
Content-Type: {{jsonContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "city": "Barcelona",
  "foundedYear": 1899,
  "name": "FC Barcelona"
}

###
@teamId = {{createTeam.response.body.data.id}}

### Get Team
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}
Content-Type: {{jsonContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update Team
PATCH  {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}
Content-Type: {{jsonContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

